    "plain_content":  "Trouble viewing this email? View in browser ( {{Weblink}} )\n\n*TIME TO GET* *SPOOKY!*\n\nThe Halloween Edition\nOctober 2019\n\n*FEATURED RECIPE*\nTrick or Treat(s)\n\nHoney Butter Cookies\nLearn the secret ingredient in these special treats that make them scary good!\n\n*READ NOW →* ( http://www.google.com )\n\n*FAMILY FUN*\nFor the Ghosts \u0026 Ghouls\n\nPumpkin Carving Patterns\nGet the whole family involved in creating artistic pumpkins that are a cut above the rest.\n\n*READ NOW →* ( http://www.google.com )\n\nSkeleton Face Painting Tutorial\nLast year, my son, Kaden, wanted a skeleton face for his costume. This year, I show you how.\n\n*READ NOW →* ( http://www.google.com )\n\nSee my life beyond the blog.\nVisit me on my social media channels!\n\n( http://www.facebook.com ) ( http://www.facebook.com ) ( http://www.facebook.com ) ( www.google.com )\n\n{{Sender_Name}}\n\n{{Sender_Address}} , {{Sender_City}} , {{Sender_State}} {{Sender_Zip}}\n\nUnsubscribe ( {{{unsubscribe}}} ) - Unsubscribe Preferences ( {{{unsubscribe_preferences}}} )\n\n♥ POWERED BY TWILIO SENDGRID ( https://www.sendgrid.com/?utm_source=powered-by\u0026utm_medium=email )",
